name: Trayon White Sr.
bio: Trayon White Sr. is a Washington, D.C. native and longtime Ward 8 councilmember, known for his work on youth, housing, and community development.

name: Mike Austin
bio: Mike Austin is a fourth-generation Washingtonian, attorney, and former ANC 8C chair who has worked on economic development and Ward 8 public policy.

name: Sheila Bunn
bio: Sheila Bunn is a lifelong Ward 8 resident and veteran public servant with decades of experience working in Congress, the Mayor’s Office, and the D.C. Council.

name: Salim Adofo
bio: Salim Adofo is a community advocate, ANC 8C commissioner, and U.S. Army veteran focused on education, housing quality, and safety in Ward 8.
